<div class="c_DNN6 c_DNN6_Header">
	
	<div class="pc-common">
		<div class="pc-header"><h1><span id="dnn_ctr14290_dnnTitle_titleLabel" class="Head">Professional Factory Trained & ASE Certified Master Technicians</span>


</h1></div>
		<div class="pc-body">
			<div id="dnn_ctr14290_ContentPane" class="wrapper"><!-- Start_Module_14290 --><div id="dnn_ctr14290_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
	<div id="dnn_ctr14290_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
		<p>Serving the Northern Virginia area for over 15 years, <a href="http://www.currysauto.com">Curry&rsquo;s Auto Service</a> is a full service repair facility staffed by expert, ASE Certified Master Technicians, some who are factory trained.  We are a Certified Female Friendly service center.  Our teams are the go-to experts for all complicated and hard to diagnose issues.  We hire and train the best in the industry and purchase top of the line computer diagnostic equipment.  We are experts in all European, Import and Domestic vehicles and perform regular maintenance, tire services, performance upgrades, VA State Safety Inspections and any service that your vehicle needs.</p>
<p>With each visit, you&rsquo;ll receive a Complementary Curry&rsquo;s Car Physical. Our goal is to provide you with the most information as possible so you can make the best, informed decision about the maintenance of your vehicle.</p>
<p>Our team of Technicians and Managers are ready to serve you and make your visit the best repair experience you&rsquo;ve ever had.  We are committed to build a relationship with you so we can assist you in maintaining the health of your vehicle.  With each purchase, you&rsquo;ll receive our Curry Warranty:</p>
<ul>
    <li>24 month/ 24,000 mile NATIONWIDE Parts and Labor Warranty</li>
    <li>6 month/ 6,000 mile Warranty on all Alignments</li>
    <li>FREE Roadside tire assistance with every purchase of Yokohama, Pirelli, Falken and select other tires. (See your invoice.)</li>
    <li>Available Road Hazard coverage on most tire purchases (extra charges my apply)</li>
</ul>
<p class="curryblue">(Exclusions:  High performance and after-market upgrades, and customer-supplied parts.)</p>
<p>
BG services have additional coverage for some of your vehicles systems. <a href="http://www.currysauto.com/services/bg-fluid-fuel-services.aspx">Click here</a> to learn more.</p>
<p>For local service, please call: 703-641-2869.</p>
<p>For out of area service, please call 800-351-8432.</p>
	</div>

</div><!-- End_Module_14290 --></div>

<div id="CatList">
    <div class="LandingPageBody"><p>We are one of the leading auto repair shops and mechanics in Gainesville, VA, Alexandria, VA, Arlington, VA, and other surrounding areas.
